[taskcluster 2017-12-04T18:53:35.685Z]       "release": "https://github.com/taskcluster/generic-worker/releases/tag/v10.0.5", [taskcluster 2017-12-04T18:53:35.685Z]       "version": "10.0.5" [taskcluster 2017-12-04T18:53:35.685Z]     }, [taskcluster 2017-12-04T18:53:35.685Z]     "machine-setup": { [taskcluster 2017-12-04T18:53:35.685Z]       "ami-created": "2017-12-04 17:46:11.070Z",
